"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/89477","HM Treasury","false","2014-09-03","<p>I refer my hon, Friend to the answer that I gave on 11 February 2014, Hansard, columns 212-14WH.</p>","South West Hertfordshire","Mr David Gauke",,"2014-09-03T13:51:03.5665816Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/89477/answer","Biography information for Mr David Gauke","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/89477/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/89477/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2014-08-29","Hotels: VAT","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, if he will bring forward proposals to reduce VAT to five per cent on hotel rooms.","false","Biography information for Henry Smith","Crawley","Henry Smith","207515"
